OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779898263
OL,3,CJersey Women reclaim the 2026 Muratti
OL,4,CVase
OL,6,FAfter two consecutive defeats, Jersey
OL,7,FFA Women have reclaimed the Muratti
OL,8,FVase from Guernsey by a 6-1 home
OL,9,Fvictory at Springfield.
OL,11,FJersey led 2-0 at the break but scored
OL,12,Ffour more in the second half to record
OL,13,Fone of the largest Muratti victories
OL,14,Fin recent years.
OL,16,FThe victory denied Guernsey a historic
OL,17,Fthird Muratti win and prevented the
OL,18,Fisland from winning back-to-back
OL,19,Fvictories in both the men's and
OL,20,Fwomen's fixtures.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
