FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779898263
OL,3,CJersey Women reclaim the 2026 Muratti
OL,4,CVase
OL,6,FCommenting on the team's success, Chad
OL,7,FMorris, Jersey FA's Women's manager,
OL,8,Fsays: "It was a dominant win, that is
OL,9,Fby far the most dominant performance
OL,10,Fwe have ever seen the Jersey side.
OL,12,F"Take the score out, but just how we
OL,13,Fperformed, everyone stuck to the game
OL,14,Fplan and just dominated from start to
OL,15,Ffinish. I am just so proud of the
OL,16,Fplayers."
OL,18,FLast year saw Jersey lose 2-1 to the
OL,19,FGreens; however, this year's Muratti
OL,20,Fsaw the team lift the trophy in front
OL,21,Fof a home crowd.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779898263
OL,3,CJersey Women reclaim the 2026 Muratti
OL,4,CVase
OL,6,FScoring the first goal was Jersey's
OL,7,FLeah Morris, followed by Roisin Flynn,
OL,8,Fwho doubled the lead with a strike
OL,9,Ffrom 20 yards.
OL,11,FIt was then Jersey skipper Holly
OL,12,FSundby who scored the third and fourth
OL,13,Fgoals for the team.
OL,15,FThe second half saw the Greens kick
OL,16,Fback as Ruby Smith headed the ball
OL,17,Finto the net, securing Guernsey's only
OL,18,Fgoal of the afternoon.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
