OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779898263
OL,3,CJersey Women reclaim the 2026 Muratti
OL,4,CVase
OL,6,FSecuring the title, Shana Dolbel and
OL,7,FAnita Tavares scored the final goals,
OL,8,Fthe game ending with a 6-1 win.
OL,10,FMaking her debut for the team, player
OL,11,Fof the match and goal scorer, Shana
OL,12,FDolbel says: "It feels amazing, it
OL,13,Ffeels great to be here, and I couldn't
OL,14,Fhave asked for more."
OL,16,F"The energy around this team is crazy,
OL,17,Fit is just so good. The whole team
OL,18,Fgave such a good performance, I
OL,19,Fwouldn't say one person had a bad
OL,20,Fgame."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779898263
OL,3,CJersey Women reclaim the 2026 Muratti
OL,4,CVase
OL,6,FGuernsey FC Women's manager, Anna
OL,7,FGauvain, says: "It is always
OL,8,Fdisappointing losing a Muratti, but at
OL,9,Fthe end of the day, the better team
OL,10,Fwon.
OL,12,F"We didn't show up today, and that's
OL,13,Fwhat happens in a Muratti when one
OL,14,Fteam is here, and the other one is
OL,15,Fstruggling a little bit today. I don't
OL,16,Fknow why, we will go away and think
OL,17,Fabout that.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779898263
OL,3,CJersey Women reclaim the 2026 Muratti
OL,4,CVase
OL,6,F"Fair play to Jersey, some big players
OL,7,Fback for them and unfortunately, we
OL,8,Fwere missing a couple. The better team
OL,9,Fwon.
OL,11,F"It wasn't quite working today, and I
OL,12,Fam not sure why. I think the heat
OL,13,Faffected some of the girls, but fair
OL,14,Fplay for Jersey."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
